TigerVNC 1.16.2 security release. Posted by Alan Coopersmith on Mar 26I don't see a CVE id listed, but the fix appears to be pretty simple:

 shminfo->shmid = shmget(IPC_PRIVATE,
 xim->bytes_per_line * xim->height,
- IPC_CREAT|0777);
+ IPC_CREAT|0600);

